theorem isHomeomorph_of_isClosed_injection {X Y : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] [TopologicalSpace Y]
  [LocallyCompactSpace Y] [T2Space Y] {f : X → Y}
  (hf : IsClosed (Set.range f)) (hfi : Function.Injective f) :
  Homeomorph X (Subtype (Set.range f)) := by
  sorry
